Description: Papyrus fragment bearing 3 lines of a Coptic text written against the fibres (verso). Perhaps same papyrus as 75382 and 75384? EA 75376, 75377, 75378, 75379, 75380, 75381, 75382, 75383, 75384, 75385, 75386, 75387, 75388 are mounted together.
